## ğŸ§ª 6. Sample SQL Queries

```sql
-- 1. List all countries in Asia
SELECT name FROM country
JOIN continent ON country.continent_id = continent.continent_id
WHERE continent.name = 'Asia';

-- 2. Top 5 most populated cities
SELECT name, population
FROM city
ORDER BY population DESC
LIMIT 5;

-- 3. Countries with official English language
SELECT country.name
FROM country
JOIN language ON country.country_id = language.country_id
WHERE language.name = 'English' AND language.is_official = 'Yes';

-- 4. Number of cities per country
SELECT country.name, COUNT(city.city_id) AS num_cities
FROM country
JOIN city ON country.country_id = city.country_id
GROUP BY country.name;

